                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9623" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0432</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1170 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从画地为牢到连横共赢：R公司组织结构的嬗变</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Decentralization to Collaboration: Transmutation of the organizational structure of Company R</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">张识宇，刘玉洁，曹丽荣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">苏州利华科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">生产运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织结构；组织设计；事业部制结构；矩阵制结构；组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">organizational structure；organizational design；divisional structure；matrix structure；organizational change</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">R公司是一家中型民营EMS企业，历经20年的发展，在长三角地区颇具影响力。2021年R公司内外环境剧烈变化，出现了资源利用率低、横向协调差、效率低下等问题。案例对R公司的经营问题进行描述，对组织结构进行诊断，发现组织结构不足以支持公司发展和战略实施。按照发现问题、研究问题、解决问题的思路，描述了公司进行组织结构优化的背景、过程及内容，提出了矩阵制组织结构及配套的管理制度。案例首先分析了事业部制组织结构下公司出现的问题、进行组织结构诊断、接着按照确定优化目标、职能优化分解、组织结构框架优化的程序，根据组织结构设计的6个关键要素对组织结构4个方面的内容进行优化设计，并进行了运行保障调整与修正，确保新的组织结构可以有效施行。通过对本案例的学习，学生可以了解组织结构优化的步骤，掌握组织结构设计的内容和关键要素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Company R is a medium-sized private EMS company. In 2021, the company&#39;s strategy was adjusted and problems such as poor horizontal coordination and inefficiency emerged. The case described the problems of Company R, diagnosed the organizational structure, and found that the organizational structure was insufficient. According to the idea of problem identification, problem study and problem solving, it describes the background, process and content of organizational structure optimization of Company R, and proposes the matrix system organizational structure and supporting management system. The case first analyzes the problems and conducts organizational structure diagnosis, then follows the procedures of defining optimization objectives, functional optimization decomposition, and organizational structure framework optimization, and optimizes the design of four aspects of the organizational structure according to the six key elements, and makes operational guarantee adjustments and refinements. Through this case study, students can understand the steps of organizational structure optimization and master the content and key elements of organizational structure design.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《组织行为学》、《组织理论与设计》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">组织结构；组织设计；组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
